(en) Then I had a much better idea!
Puis j'ai eu une bien meilleure idée !
(en) Burger Island is the ideal place!"

(en) The sea contains only 60 micrograms\nof iodine per liter.
La mer ne contient que 60 microgrammes \nd'iode par litre.

(en) The smell of the sea is not that
of iodine, but that of dimethyl
sulfide, which comes from the
decomposition of algae.
